OL,5, P&O Ferries boss should resign over the
OL,6, no-notice sackings of 800 staff, the   
OL,7, transport secretary has said.          
OL,9,FGrant Shapps called for chief executive
OL,10,FPeter Hebblethwaite to step down after 
OL,11,Fhis "brazen" and "breathtaking"        
OL,12,Fcomments about "knowingly breaking the 
OL,13,Flaw" by not consulting staff.          
OL,15,FMr Hebblethwaite admitted to MPs that  
OL,16,Fhe broke the law but said he would make
OL,17,Fthe same decision again if he had to.  
OL,19,F"I think he should go," Mr Shapps told 
OL,20,FBBC Breakfast.                         
